=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">耳鼻咽喉科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1900</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">麻醉科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2000</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">临床病理科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2100</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">检验医学科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2200</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">放射科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2300</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">超声医学科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2400</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">核医学科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2800</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">口腔全科</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2</span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"99\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2500</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"219\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">放射肿瘤医学</span></span></p></td><td style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; text-align: justify;\" width=\"147\"><p style=\"outline: none;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2</span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); clear: both; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">注：以上招生人数含单位委培及面向社会招收人员，协同单位除专科医院外其他招生指标未入本表格，请进一步单独浏览协同单位（综合医院）的招生简章。<br/>&nbsp;<br/><strong>（二）、报名条件</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">1、政治思想好，身体健康，自愿参加规范化培训，服从医院工作安排；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">2、具有临床医学、口腔医学各专业本科及以上学历毕业生；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">3、已从事临床医疗工作并获得执业医师资格，需要接受培训的人员及其他需要接受培训的人员。<br/>&nbsp;<br/><strong>（三）、报名时间</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">本简章公布之日至4月30日止。<br/>&nbsp;<br/><strong>（四）、报名办法</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">1、报名资料<br/>（1）《2019年汕头大学医学院第一附属医院住院医师规范化培训学员报名表》(附件1);<br/>（2）个人简历；<br/>（3）本科毕业生：身份证、毕业证、学位证（应届生提供在校证明及学生证）、四/六级英语考试合格证书、<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">个人成绩单</span>；<br/>（4）硕、博士毕业生：除以上资料外另交本科毕业后临床工作时间和临床轮训<br/>考核证明；<br/>（5）执业医师资格证、执业证（已获得该两证者需提供）。<br/><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">（</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">6）既往参加住院医师规范化培训轮科及考核证明材料（并轨参加规培的专业学位研究生或往届生有培训基地工作经历人员，须加盖培训基地公章）。</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">2、报名办法<br/>（1）网络报名：<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">登录广东省住院医师规范化培训管理平台（</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">http://zl2.gdzpgl.net:8088/guip/</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">），首次登陆先自行注册，选择“培训学员入口”完成网络报名。</span><br/>（2）&nbsp;<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">提交材料：学员完成网络报名后将以上</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">报名</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">材料扫描件或电子版按顺序压缩</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">成一个</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">文件（文件命名：</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">201</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">9住培报名</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">+</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">姓名</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">+</span><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">专业）于报名截止日期前发送至</span>sdfygpzs@163.com邮箱。<br/><strong>（五）、招录程序</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">1、初步审核通过学员，我院于5月份另行通知考试时间（邮件、官网），<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">请保持关注官网及邮件回复情况。</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">2、考核事项：<br/>（1）考试时间：5月，具体按通知。<br/>（2）考试内容：<br/>笔试：专业知识（医学基础及临床医学知识），权重60%。<br/>面试：临床思维、应变、表达能力等，权重40%。</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">3、&nbsp;招录公示：</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">录取名单于结束考核5个工作日在汕头大学医学院第一附属医院住院医师规范化培训过程管理系统网站（http://218.16.214.141:9005/）通知公告栏公示。<br/><strong>（六）、招收条件</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">根据考试结果及临床培训经历等综合得分，按照“公开公平、择优录取、双</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">向选择”原则确定培训对象，额满为止。未招满额的培训学科，根据报名人员自愿服从调剂培训方向进行重新分配。<br/><strong>（七）、学员待遇</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">1、<span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">不需缴纳培训费；</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">2、签订《培训协议》；&nbsp;</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">3、根据《住院医师规范化培训管理办法（试行）》及广东省卫计委相关规定，每月按时发放工资，购买社会保险、医疗保险等、享有法定节假日及相关福利；</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">4、办理执业医师考试及注册管理手续；</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"background-attachment: initial; background-clip: initial; background-image: initial; background-origin: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-size: initial;\">5、人事管理 &nbsp;</span><br/>（1）社会学员：实行人事代理制度，<span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">工龄连续计算，享受国家规定的基本社会保险，工资待遇包括绩效工资和住培补助等；</span>&nbsp;<br/><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.1pt;\">（2）单位委托培养学员：由委托培养单位管理人事档案、发放基本工资及购买基本社会保险，培训基地发放住培补助等；</span></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">6、完成规范化培训并考核合格者，颁发由国家卫计委统一印制的《住院医师规范化培训合格证书》；</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">7、培训结束后社会学员可择优留院工作。<br/><strong>（八）、联系方式：</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">联&nbsp;系&nbsp;人：吴汉生老师、杨瑨老师、郑茵老师&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">联系电话：0754-88905387/88905376</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">电子邮箱:&nbsp; sdfygpzs@163.com</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">医院网站：<a href=\"http://www.stuh.com.cn/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\">http://www.stuh.com.cn/</span></a></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">基地住院医师规范化培训管理网站：<a href=\"http://218.16.214.141:9005/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\">http://218.16.214.141:9005</span></a></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">联系地址：广东省汕头市金平区长平路57号汕头大学医学院第一附属医院规培办公室</span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">邮政编码：515041<br/>&nbsp;<br/><strong>（九）、协同单位招生</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\">协同单位招生简章详见各协同单位医院官网及基地住院医师规范化培训管理网站：<a href=\"http://218.16.214.141:9005/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\">http://218.16.214.141:9005</span></a>。<br/>&nbsp;<br/>1、汕头大学医学院第二附属医院官网：<a href=\"http://www.st120.cn/\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">http://www.st120.cn</a><br/>报名联系人：王老师、陈老师。联系电话：0754-88915817<br/>2、汕头大学医学院附属